OL,3,CBlaenavon murder: Man appears in court
OL,4,Ccharged with killing 'champ' boxer
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court accused of
OL,7,Fthe murder of a talented boxer and MMA
OL,8,Ffighter.
OL,10,FKai Pennell, 34, of Blaenavon, has
OL,11,Fbeen charged with murdering Duane
OL,12,FKeen, 47, also from Blaenavon, last
OL,13,Fweek.
OL,15,FThe defendant also faces an allegation
OL,16,Fof criminal damage and making threats
OL,17,Fto kill and appeared at Newport Crown
OL,18,FCourt on Tuesday morning, 21 October,
OL,19,Ffor a brief hearing, during which he
OL,20,Fspoke only to confirm his name, date
OL,21,Fof birth, and address.
