OL,6,FA provisional trial date was scheduled
OL,7,Ffor 13 April and Pennell will reappear
OL,8,Fin court for a plea and trial
OL,9,Fpreparation hearing on 21 November,
OL,10,FJudge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke said.
OL,12,FShe told the defendant, of Riverside
OL,13,FDrive, that he would be remanded in
OL,14,Fcustody while he awaited those dates.
OL,16,FThere was some disorder in the court
OL,17,Fduring the brief hearing on Tuesday
OL,18,Fmorning during which the judge had to
OL,19,Fremind members of the public gallery
OL,20,Fthat they should leave the court if
OL,21,Fthey couldn't behave.
