OL,6,FShe said: "Understandably, feelings
OL,7,Fare running very high but I also have
OL,8,Fno doubt (...) people will be able to
OL,9,Fcontrol themselves. If people find
OL,10,Fthey can't control themselves then the
OL,11,Fbest thing to do is to step outside."
OL,13,FMr Keen was discovered with serious
OL,14,Finjuries and pronounced dead at an
OL,15,Faddress in Riverside Drive, Blaenavon,
OL,16,Fin the early hours of Friday, 17
OL,17,FOctober.
