OL,6,FWitnesses reported seeing armed police
OL,7,Fand other officers arrive at Riverside
OL,8,FDrive shortly after 2am, along with a
OL,9,Fpolice helicopter circling overhead.
OL,11,FParamedics, armed police and the Wales
OL,12,FAir Ambulance were in attendance and
OL,13,Fthe street was cordoned off.
OL,15,FPaying tribute, Mr Keen's family said
OL,16,Fhe was a great boxer and MMA all
OL,17,Frounder "with lots of belts to his
OL,18,Fname".
